513
00:42:16,715 --> 00:42:17,477
[SPEAKER_09]: well as training.

514
00:42:17,557 --> 00:42:21,646
[SPEAKER_09]: Let Crystal answer that.

515
00:42:21,867 --> 00:42:23,491
[SPEAKER_02]: Just to pick up a couple of points that have come up.

516
00:42:23,531 --> 00:42:28,943
[SPEAKER_02]: On public service investment, just to be clear about that, the NHS is receiving more money than it has ever received in history.

517
